{
  "texts": [
    "In the realm of medical image analysis, Sarah Ali et al.",
    "(Ismael et al. 2020) introduced an advanced approach that harnesses the power of Residual Networks (ResNets) for brain tumor classification.",
    "Their study involved a comprehensive evaluation on a 11 Page 26 of 33 benchmark dataset comprising 3064 MRI images of three distinct brain tumor types.",
    "Impressively, their model achieved a remarkable accuracy of 99%, surpassing previous works in the same domain.",
    "Shifting focus to the domain of remote sensing, Xiaowei et al. (2020) embarked on a deep learning journey for remote sensing image classification."
  ]
}